item.dc:creator: Kaze
item.description:
You do realize that the majority of those are never, ever used, right?

External rail accessories are nothing but a burden and add extra weight to the system. But then again something tells me the OP is one of those 12 year olds who plays CSS and skins his weapons to have every attachment and accessory under the sun.

I would go for the scope,grenade launcher,retracktable buttstock,pistol grip and one of those drill like things.that`s all I need to be a good AUTO sniper

You’d also need a clue and some cognitive ability.

Either of which you seem to have.
